text.tspan: GDP per head vs share of agriculture in employment, 1801 to 2010
The vertical axis shows historical estimates of the employment share in the agriculture sector. The horizontal axis
shows GDP per head after adjusting for inflation (figures are in 1990 international Geary–Khamis dollars.)
GDP per capita in 1990 Int. GK$ (Maddison-Project 2013)
Source: Maddison-Project (2013), Our World In Data based on Herrendorf et al. (2014) and GGDC-10 (2015)
